WEBVTT

00:04:25.872 --> 00:04:30.111
There will be the obligatory coconut tree,
banana tree, orangutan.

00:04:30.135 --> 00:04:31.349
(Laughter)

00:04:31.373 --> 00:04:33.334
And the orangutan doesn't even get paid.

00:04:33.358 --> 00:04:34.532
(Laughter)

00:04:35.405 --> 00:04:39.353
Look at how we represent ourselves.
Look at how we represent nature.

00:04:39.377 --> 00:04:41.368
Look at how we represent the countryside.

00:04:41.392 --> 00:04:44.670
Look at how we represent
agricultural life.

00:04:44.694 --> 00:04:46.675
Watch our sitcoms.

00:04:46.699 --> 00:04:49.632
Watch our dramas. Watch our movies.

00:04:49.656 --> 00:04:53.266
It's very common,
particularly in Southeast Asia,

00:04:53.290 --> 00:04:56.546
when you watch these sitcoms,

00:04:56.570 --> 00:05:01.812
if there's someone from the countryside,
invariably, they're ugly,